test_large_range:
assert [86, 87, 88, 89] == [88, 89]
  At index 0 diff: 86 != 88
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 88
  Full diff:
  - [88, 89]
  + [86, 87, 88, 89]
test_even_range:
assert [172, 174, 176, 178] == [176, 178]
  At index 0 diff: 172 != 176
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 176
  Full diff:
  - [176, 178]
  + [172, 174, 176, 178]
